title: Physically Active Adults, United Kingdom, 2008/09
name: Physically Active Adults, United Kingdom, 2008/09
description: Association of Public Health Observatories publishes data on adults participating in recommended levels of physical activity. The purpose is to to estimate prevalence of physical activity beneficial to health in the population. To monitor the effectiveness of programmes aiming to increase participation of adults in sport and active recreation.
